---
title: Savoury Steak with Shallot Gravy, Crispy Roasted Potatoes and Creamed Kale
description: Creamy shallot gravy over juicy steak is dinner perfection. It’s impossible to mess up, yet bound to impress! Classic roasted potatoes and our healthy version of creamed kale complete this cozy dish.
